values.Script:
CALL NEW LEAD PHONE SCRIPT (BASIC)
Hello member('First Name') , this is ${submitterName} from Gracie Barra Jiu-Jitsu; how are you doing?

I just got a request for a free class from you. Do you have a couple of minutes for us to find the best time for you? Are you inquiring about classes for yourself or someone else?

Do you have any previous martial art experience?

We are offering an Intro class at no charge to you. This would be a great opportunity to come to the school, meet the instructors, meet the other students, and, of course, have a better understanding of what Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu is about. During the lesson, the instructor will evaluate your skill level to recommend the best program for you.

When would be the best time for you to come to the school, early morning, noon, or evenings?

Got it! I have mornings / afternoon / evening available on _______ and ______, which one would be best for you?

Great! I have you scheduled for ____________, and if you could please arrive 10 minutes earlier would be great.

What is the best phone number to contact you to send some important information to have the best experience in your first class?

Would you like to bring a friend to the class with you?

Thank you! Once again, my name is ${submitterName}. Call me if you need anything else. ${submitterName}. Have a great day!
